quran[38]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Si darotoongal ngal darike
  56,2,alanaa daragol maggal ngol fennoowo
  56,3,"Hoyfin…óinayngal (yeddu…ďe), …ďamtayngal (gom…óim…ďe)"
  56,4,Si leydi ndin dilliniraama dillannde
  56,5,pelle …óen munciroyee muncannde
  56,6,…óe wonta collaari ruuynayndi
  56,7,wattinon nooneeji tati
  56,8,Ko wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďen - iskin …ďen yim…ďe √Īaamo
  56,9,"e wontiroo…ďe nano …ďen, bis e …ďen yim…ďe nano"
  56,10,"Ko adondiraynoo…ďe …ďen (e mo∆ī∆īere ka aduna), adoytee (naadeede Aljanna)"
  56,11,Ko …ďen woni badnitaa…ďe …ďen
  56,12,ka Aljannaaji neeminii…ói
  56,13,"dental jeyaangal e [mofte] adinoo…ďe …ďen"
  56,14,"e see…óaa…ďe jeyaa…ďe e [mofte] sakkitii…ďe …ďen"
  56,15,"hi…ďe e hoore dan…óe yu…ď…ďiraa…óe [kaŇčŇče]"
  56,16,"hara hi…ďe so…ď…ďindii e majje, fewtondir…ďe"
  56,17,Sukaa…ďe duuminaa…ďe hino wanngoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe
  56,18,"wonndude e √Īeddu…óe, e cataloy, e koroy e [hebbiniraakoy] beere ilaynde"
  56,19,"…ďe muusetaake ko*e nder ton, …ďe siwritaa"
  56,20,e muuyantee…ói …ói …ďe su…ďotoo
  56,21,e teewu colli ngu …ďe tuuyatee
  56,22,e huurul'aynii…ďe -yaaja gite en
  56,23,nanndu…ďe e kaŇčŇče lu'lu'u maraa…óe
  56,24,njo…ďdi ko …ďe gollaynoo kon
  56,25,"∆Āe nanataa nder ton haala meere, wanaa ko bakkondiŇčta"
  56,26,"si wanaa wi'aneede : \"Salaaman! Salaaman!\" [Sa…ói mon! sa…ói mon]"
  56,27,"E wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďen, ko woni …ďen yim…ďe √Īaamo"
  56,28,"[∆Āe wonay] e le…ó…óe jaa…ďe new…óu…óe"
  56,29,e banaanaje fawandir…óe
  56,30,e …óowdi duumiindi
  56,31,e ndiyam juuray…óam
  56,32,e …ďi…ó…ďe le…ó…óe …óuu…óu…óe
  56,33,…óe ta∆īondirtaa …óe ha…óetaake
  56,34,e dan…óe …ďamtaa…óe
  56,35,Ko Menen tagi fu…ó…ói …ďe
  56,36,Men wa…ói …ďe curbaa…ďe-boomi
  56,37,"yi…óu…ďe wor…ďe mun, goree…ďe"
  56,38,"[Men marani …ďe] yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen"